window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Being popular is such a drain....</p> <p>Someone is supping upon young noblemen, and it's up to Hannah and Wycliff to investigate. But how to catch the killer? If it is indeed a vampyre, known for their impeccable fashion sense, nocturnal roaming, and dislike of rain...it could be anyone among dozens of fops and dandies.</p> <p>With her best friend's wedding imminent, Hannah is determined that the event be untouched by murder or mayhem. To ensure a magical fairy-tale event, they must catch the murderer before the big day. This pursuit will unearth long-buried secrets and Hannah and Wycliff face their greatest challenge yet...socializing....</p>"; 
